Rama Rama Sai Ram Sita Rama Radhe Shyam (3)
 Dasharatha Nandana Sita Ram Vasudeva Nandana Radhe Shyam
 Ishwaramba Nandana Parthi Purishwara Sai Ram (2)

 Chant the name of Rama, Lord of Sita and son of King Dasharatha;
 Chant the name of Krishna, Lord of Radha and son of Vasudeva;
 Chant the name of Sai of Puttaparthi, son of Eshwaramma
